{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Camille and Laura is a short narrative game about the daily life of a single mother. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129110/extras/Godot_v4.1.2-stable_win64_RclLCfmKjx.gif?t=1740197121\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It\u2019s Camille\u2019s first week of elementary school, one of the most important weeks in someone's life. Take the role of Laura, Camille\u2019s mother, as she tries her best to be an exemplary mother for her small family. Navigate your work environment, do daily chores, and try as you might to raise your kid the best way you can. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Camille and Laura is an honest look at the realities of life and daily struggles. Solo developed and inspired by children shows, I wanted to make a game that could be both filled with fun, childish excitement, while recognizing the extreme isolation and grind of adult life. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This a short narrative game that will take under an hour and a half to complete. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129110/extras/Steam2_570x310.gif?t=1740197121\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hand-drawn graphics </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A narrative adventure with dialogue options and branching paths </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Point and click interactions </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Daily chores and work </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Bed time stories </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Some good gags, even more bad ones </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">An honest look at the reality of human existence </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">At least one fun giraffe</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_para